bilingual.source: We received a cable from the headquarters.

bilingual.source: The UN headquarters is located in New York City.

The headquarters of this group is in New York.
bilingual.target: 这个集团的总部设在纽约。

bilingual.source: Do you know where Nissan's headquarters are?
bilingual.target: 你知道日产的总部在哪里吗？

yingyinNormal.en: You're not in Headquarters. Without you, Riley can't be happy. We got to get you back up there.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你不在大脑总部，没有了你，莱莉就没办法开心起来了，我们得把你送回总部。

yingyinNormal.en: Thanks. This will make it a lot easier to walk back to Headquarters.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢谢，这样走回总部就容易多了。

yingyinNormal.en: This is the Nut. The Capitol's headquarters for our offensive operations.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是基地中心，是国会区总部为我们进攻而设立的。

yingyinNormal.en: We'll be back to Headquarters before she wakes up. We'll just go across Friendship Island.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们要在她醒来前到达总部，我们只需要跨过友谊岛。

yingyinNormal.en: And I think I know why. The prototype 5K tower was built at their corporate headquarters.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想这就是原因了，5K塔的原型就建在他们的公司总部。

yingyinNormal.en: Bing Bong says it's the quickest way to Headquarters. No. But Joy, this is abstract thought.
yingyinNormal.zh: 冰棒说这是回总部最快的方法。不，但是"乐乐"，这是抽象思维。

yingyinNormal.en: Chicago KSI headquarters is like a fortress. I'm gonna find a way into their top-secret military wing.
yingyinNormal.zh: KSI芝加哥总部就像一座堡垒，我会想办法混入最高军事机密区。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, hey, Don't be sad. Tell you what. When I get back up to Headquarters, I'll make sure Riley remembers you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 嗯，嗯，别伤心，听我说，等我回到总部，我会让莱莉再次想起你的。

yingyinNormal.en: The manuals? The manuals. You read the manuals? Yeah. So you know the way back to headquarters. I guess. Woo-Hnn!
yingyinNormal.zh: 手册？手册，你读过手册？是的。那么你知道回总部的路。我猜是。太好了！

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, here we go. We'll be back to Headquarters before morning. We can do it. This will be easy! This is working.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好了，出发，我们能在天亮前回到总部，我们能做到的，这很容易！这方法很管用。

yingyinNormal.en: We can fix this. We just have to get back to Headquarters, plug the core memories in and Riley will be back to normal.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们...我们可以解决这个问题，我们只要先回到大脑总部把这些核心记忆球放回去，莱莉就能恢复正常了。

yingyinNormal.en: And as soon as we return to the North Wind headquarters, grab fresh equipment, and work up a smashing new plan, we'll come speeding back and take down Dave.
yingyinNormal.zh: 只要我们回到北风总部，拿到最新的设备，设想一个粉碎性的新计划，我们就会速速回来将戴夫拿下。

yingyinNormal.en: The HeForShe conference was watched over 11 million times, sparking 1.2 billion social media conversations, culminating in the HeForShe hashtag becoming so popular that Twitter painted it on the walls of its headquarters.
yingyinNormal.zh: HeForShe会议有超过1100万的浏览量，引起了12亿的社交网站讨论量，HeForShe的话题是如此流行，以至于推特把它漆在了总部的墙上。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《艾玛·沃特森达沃斯世界经济论坛HeForShe演讲》

yingyinNormal.en: And that was just the beginning. Headquarters only got more crowded from there.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这仅仅是个开始，指挥部从此之后变得越来越拥挤了。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: His status in Lord Wellington’s <highlight>headquarters</highlight> were all bound up with the class politics of the army at the time.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他在威灵顿勋爵司令部的地位与当时军队的阶级政治息息相关。

examination_example.sentence: And whose secrets had been revealed by the work of one George Scovell, an officer in British <highlight>headquarters</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这些文件的秘密被英国总部的一位军官乔治·斯科维尔揭露出来。
